     FGAEPL01 IP  E           K        DISK
     FGAEPR02 O   E             20     PRINTER
     E                    MSG     1   1 30
     IGAEPL011    01
     C           *IN10     IFEQ '0'
     C                     MOVE MSG,1     TYTL
     C                     SETON                     09
     C                     WRITEGAEPR021
     C                     SETOF                     09
     C                     END
     C           FASKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C           FASKHZ    ANDLE*DATE
     C                     ELSE
     C           CNT       IFEQ 5
     C                     WRITEGAEPR021
     C                     Z-ADD0         CNT
     C                     END
     C                     WRITEGAEPR022
     C                     ADD  1         CNT     10
     C                     END
     C                     SETON                     10
**  MSG
QUENCHING FURNACE ABLTY M LIST
